social_posts.post_text:
🎬 AND IT'S OFFICIAL 🎬

In so glad I don't have to hold this in any longer...

I was selected as a New Orleans Hero for the Emmy winning Netflix series Queer Eye that premieres May 12! 🤯⚜️❤️🏳️‍🌈

This experience was honest, emotional, and LIFE CHANGING!!!

Many of you will get to see me on such a vulnerable human level, a level you've never known me before... and yeah I'm not going to lie that scares me ALOT....BUT my hope is that it touches and inspires people!

This series will seriously touch your heart! ❤️

I hope you share, shout, grab a group of friends and all tune in and watch! 

Love you guys ALWAYS and thank you for the support!

I'll continue to release some content leading up to the premiere so STAY TUNED! ⚜️❤️🏳️‍🌈

⚜️ FEEL GOOD FRIDAY ⚜️

How is this post for some Feel Good Friday positive vibes! 😍

You guys know how much I LOVE @fleurty_girl ... so when they asked me to fill in for #PrideMonth I jumped at the opportunity! 😁

Well.... they COMPLETELY SURPRISED this week with my VERY OWN SAINT CANDLE 😭😭😭😭....How incredible! 🤯

To say this blew me away with so much love TRULY ISN'T SAYING ENOUGH.... 🥹

If you'd be interested in purchasing a Saint Nola Steph Candle where a portion of the proceeds go to charity check out FG's post and let them know!

Thank you again EVERYONE for the love and support!!! 🥰⚜️❤️🏳️‍🌈

#QueerEye
#FleurtyGirl
#NolaSteph
#SuperfanSteph
#FeelGoodFriday

🏳️‍🌈 CAMP OUT FLORIDA 🏳️‍⚧️

As many of you saw on my live today...

I am so humbled and honored to be able to partner with and be an Ambassador for THE BEST LGBTQIA+ YOUTH CAMP in the U.S.! 

@campout.florida is a non-profit that offers a week long overnight summer camp providing a space for adventure,  experiences, and the authentic expression of LGBTQ+ youth and their allies. ALL are WELCOME & RESPECTED! 🥰🏳️‍🌈🏳️‍⚧️

Please take the opportunity to give CAMP OUT Florida a follow,  share their message, and encourage family members to SIGN UP for the 2024 camp.... it'll fill up faster than you know! 💯

There's also several sponsorship level opportunities for businesses that want to help MAKE A DIFFERENCE! ❤️

I absolutely love and believe that camps like this CAN CHANGE & ENHANCE LIVES! So please,  go check them out and support however you can TODAY! 😍

Hoping everyone and their families were able to enjoy Independence Day and the first week of July! 

The pups weren't thrilled about my July 4th Ameri-cat shirt 🤣, but I got some love anyways! 🥰⚜️🇺🇸❤️🏳️‍🌈🏳️‍⚧️

🏳️‍🌈 ONE YEAR SINCE FILMING 🏳️‍🌈

Can you guys believe it's been 1 year since @jvn @karamo @antoni @bobby @tanfrance  came into my life, as we started filming for Netflix @queereye Season 7 New Orleans!

I didn't know what to expect going into filming,  but these amazing humans completely CHANGED MY LIFE!

Walking out the FAB 5 truck for my "Reveal" felt OUT OF BODY! (and not just because Tan gave me a big shake 🤣)

I can't thank EVERYONE enough for all of the love, sharing, and support of this show,  my journey, and ALL OF THE HEROES that were a part of this season! ❤️

What were your favorite and/or funniest moments from the episode? 👀

⚜️ HUGS & LOVE FROM NOLA ⚜️

💍 1 Year Since OUR ENGAGEMENT 💍

The BEST MOMENT of MY ENTIRE LIFE happened a year ago....

My best friend,  my love,  and the person that ALWAYS SEES THE BEST IN ME "SAID YES" to being my life partner!

Every day I'm with her I truly feel blessed beyond words! 🥹

I had the ring and was going back and forth on whether to actually do it.... NOBODY KNEW but the producer, so to say I was shaking was an understatement 😭  But knowing our family and friends were ALL IN THIS ONE PLACE,  told me this was right!

Thank you @raecain07 for being the BEST PERSON I KNOW and for loving me through my ups and downs... I'll love you FOREVER! ❤️

🥂 DRAG BRUNCH FUN 🥂

Sundays are meant for DRAG BRUNCH!!!

@debbiewithad and @laveaucontraire came to slay and keep us dancing and laughing this past Sunday!

Such a fun time with @rulavincent81 @bvince and @exhausted_witch at @saintjohnnola ❤️

The food was DELISH and the bottomless Bloody Mary's & Mimosas were a great pairing! Well definitely be bringing @raecain07 back here... it was SO GOOD!

Do yourself a favor and support local DRAG when you can.... so many entertainers in the city to have a FANTASTIC time with that are guaranteedto make you smile! 🥰

Can't wait until the next one!!! ⚜️❤️

#SupportLocalDrag
#DragIsNotACrime
#NolaNoms
#HappyPlate

I am so excited and humbled that @glorioussport in the UK reached out to me to do a story on my @queereye experience and my love for sports! 

If you have a minute today, please check out the link below and give them a like on FB & IG! 

They are ALL ABOUT elevating women's sport and Fandom, which is continuing to GROW & BLOSSOM!

😊⚜️❤️

https://glorioussport.com/articles/fandom-steph-williams-queer-eye-sports-fan

Here's to 40!  So blessed to be celebrating in paradise with @raecain07 ❤️

Thank you ALL for the birthday wishes!!!

#BlondeAndYoung

🇲🇽 Cabo San Lucas Pt. 1 Photos 🇲🇽
🏖 Life's a Beach 🏖

WOW... what a beautiful, fun, memorable, and relaxing vacation with @raecain07 at @hrhloscabos! We LOVED this resort, trip, and most IMPORTANTLY TIME TOGETHER!
❤️❤️❤️

We managed to get a couple of photos while at the resort relaxing and having fun! 🥰

Let me know if you're interested in making a trip to HRH Los Cabos (WHICH I HIGHLY RECOMMEND)...I might be able to get you a discount 😉

Cheers to 40 and the Louisiana Humidity for keeping my skin looking young 🤣⚜️❤️

social_posts.post_text:
🇲🇽 Cabo San Lucas Pt. 2 Photos 🇲🇽
🤿 The Excursion 🤿

Our sailing cruise excursion was INCREDIBLE!!!! 

We started at the marina in down Los Cabos, sailed out to Pelican Beach, Lover's Beach, and The Arch...❤️❤️❤️

We finished the day snorkeling in the Sea of Cortez, which was SO PRETTY, but it reminded me of how OUT OF SHAPE I am (almost became fish bait bc I was worn out 🤣) #JustLeaveMeHere

Taking in the views and dancing on the boat all the way back to shore... so much fun! 
(I would post videos, but I've been threatened by @raecain07 not to LOL 😘)

Lesbians Los Cabos 😎

❤️ Love & Appreciation  Post ❤️

Words CAN NOT describe how PROUD I am of this sweet lady right here! 

She's a fiance (that puts up with me 🤣)
She's a dog mom of 2
She's Trauma ICU RN
AND she continues to be a student to better herself and help others!!!!

This girl just finished her BSN and is about to go on a travel assignment to New Mexico for 3 months at another Level 1 trauma ICU!!! How UNBELIEVABLE IS SHE!? 🥰

I'm going to miss her SO MUCH,  but I'm so PROUD of the INCREDIBLE PERSON she is!

I'm beyond blessed to have her choose ME day in and day out!!!

Congrats on finishing your BSN @raecain07 
and safe travels to NM... you're going to impact so many people in a positive way!

You continue to CRUSH IT....I LOVE YOU!

❤️ Auntie Photo Dump ❤️

How incredibly blessed are @raecain07 and I to be Godparents to this sweet baby angel!? 👼

Everyone, meet Kameron! 💙💙💙

Does he not just make you smile ear to ear with happiness and joy!? 🥰

Thank you @jessfdennis and @krisden23 for coming to visit and allowing me the opportunity to finally meet Kam! 
I love you guys so much 😊❤️

Aunt Steph is ready to spoil this little man! 😁

Steph & Speedy at Saints game! ⚜️🏈❤️

Queer Eye Family! ⚜️❤️

🏳️‍🌈 FUN FLAG ALERT 🏳️‍⚧️

A new month means a NEW FLAG at the house! I couldn't run out fast enough to put our new "HUMAN" flag up... through ALL OUR DIFFERENCES, we are ALL HUMAN!

I hope as people pass by our house, this flag will serve as a reminder to BE KIND! ❤️

The visibility of INCLUSION and DIVERSITY matters NOW MORE THAN EVER! 
We are all in this together people! 💯

Happy Decadence 😎⚜️❤️🏳️‍🌈🏳️‍⚧️

⚜️ SAINTS SUNDAY w/ SPEEDY ⚜️

In honor of the @saints season starting next week...I had to share A VERY SPECIAL SUNDAY FUNDAY memory from last week. 

It was such a blessing to be able to link up with my guy speedy, his Aunt, and his coach, last weekend as we hit up the last pre-season game. 

Lots of great pictures and fun was had!

@speedy4prezident that jersey looking great on you my man! 😎

We are truly @queereye family FOR LIFE and FOREVER CONNECTED! It's more than just a show... it's a movement of INCLUSION,  GROWTH,  AND KINDNESS! 

WE. ARE. FAMILY. ⚜️🏈❤️

❤️ Steph & Rae Photo Dump ❤️

It's been a LONG time coming,  but we FINALLY got some professional photos done with the pups (Kotter & Benson) by the incredible @rachaelgobert

Life since Netflix's @queereye had been so crazy busy and we can't thank EVERYONE enough for the outpouring of love and support! 💯

Thank you to everyone that's celebrated and supported OUR LOVE over the last 7 years... we are TRULY BLESSED! 🙏🏼

Let me end by saying that I'm grateful BEYOND words that @raecain07
said YES and chooses me each and every day.  We have such a BEATUFUL life together that I NEVER take a day for granted! 🥰

MORE THINGS TO COME so you guys STAY TUNED! 😊⚜️❤️🫶🏼🏳️‍🌈

GETCHA SOME!

A Pelicans loss is ONLY TOLERABLE when you watch it with good people 💯😉

Thanks @speedy4prezident for keeping me company as Curry dropped 40 on us while eating nachos 😭🤣

Always a fun time with you, my friend ⚜️❤️

Rachael and I are beyond excited to partner with Jared to take the next step in our journey. After proposing on Queer Eye with a ring from Jared, they were kind enough to gift us our wedding bands! 💍

Thank you Jared for celebrating us and for creating a culture of inclusion to celebrate love for all ❤️

2023...
What an UNBELIEVABLY LIFE CHANGING YEAR 🤯🙏🏼

There's NOTHING that could've prepared me for EVERYTHING that's happened.

From the typical holidays, concerts, vacations, and sports events to the 1st YEAR OF: being in our new home,  being engaged,  and becoming aunts and fur-mommas again lol! 

Sprinkle in supporting others, community service, and giving back to those around me... and even that seems like a busy year!

Then came the release of Netflix's Queer Eye Season 7 New Orleans... and a piece of our story was out for the WORLD to see and share! ⚜️🏳️‍🌈❤️

There are not enough words to describe how grateful I am for literally EVERYTHING and EVERYONE (yes all of you lol)... all of the support, clicks, messages, hugs, tags, laughs, tears, lessons, stories, partnerships, and MEMORIES!

Thank you @fleurty_girl @urbansouth_nola @faubourgbeer @queereye @itv @netflix @pinknews @latimes @glorioussport @campout.florida @luxandlucajewelryco @theluminaryandco @laozi.ice.cream @pelicansnba @saints @threadbeast @wgno @grrlspot @nowthatswhaticallqueer @billyreid for your support whether through media coverage, partnerships and/or support over this past year... the kindness has been overwhelming 🙏🏼 
- please forgive me if I forgot any tags 🤦‍♀️

Thank you to my employer @coxcommunications for sharing my story with the enterprise and for providing me a platform to continue to give back and share my passion for inclusion into the new year...it's a blessing. 

Lastly... the BIGGEST thank you to the ONE PERSON that I COULD NOT have made it through 2023 without... the love of my life, my fiance @raecain07 🥹❤️
Babe it's been ONE INSANE YEAR 🤣 I love you so much and could not do this crazy life without your love,  support, and kindness.... even when it's tough love 😉 

Cheers to 2024 everyone...
THE BEST IS YET TO COME! 🥰⚜️🫶🏼
